REM windows_screenshot.duck
REM Opens the Snip & Sketch / Snipping Tool overlay via Win+Shift+S.
REM Demonstrates that a paired "keyboard" can silently capture the screen.
REM Windows 10 (1809+) and Windows 11.
REM Copy to: /sdcard/lab/ble/blueduck/scripts/

HUMAN_MODE OFF

REM Win+Shift+S — open snipping tool overlay (region select mode)
GUI-SHIFT s
